    <title>AtomicInteger自我理解与实践</title>
    <link href="/2021/08/30/AtomicInteger%E8%87%AA%E6%88%91%E7%90%86%E8%A7%A3%E4%B8%8E%E5%AE%9E%E8%B7%B5/"/>
    <url>/2021/08/30/AtomicInteger%E8%87%AA%E6%88%91%E7%90%86%E8%A7%A3%E4%B8%8E%E5%AE%9E%E8%B7%B5/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="前言"><a href="#前言" class="headerlink" title="前言"></a>前言</h1><p>记录在工作中遇到的情况:</p><ul><li>直播间中统计观看直播的人数 一开始傻傻的用<code>Integer</code>来实现 结果被<strong>汉叔</strong>说用<code>AtomicInteger</code>原子整型</li><li>我才发现我大学学的多线程只是皮毛，导致实践时根本就没考虑到高并发的情况 想都没想就之间用了Integer实现了。。。</li></ul><p>案发现场：</p><p><img src="/2021/08/30/AtomicInteger%E8%87%AA%E6%88%91%E7%90%86%E8%A7%A3%E4%B8%8E%E5%AE%9E%E8%B7%B5/image-20210831161544159.png" alt="不忍直视"></p><h1 id="AtomicInteger-原子整型"><a href="#AtomicInteger-原子整型" class="headerlink" title="AtomicInteger 原子整型"></a>AtomicInteger 原子整型</h1><div class="note note-success">            <p>原子整型在<code>java.util.concurrent.atomic</code>包下</p><p><code>AtomicInteger</code>是可以自动更新int值，有关原子变量属性的描述，一般用于用字递增<strong>计数器</strong>等应用程序中</p><p>这说明在高并发的情况下是能保证计数器不会出现不正确的情况</p>          </div><h2 id="原子性"><a href="#原子性" class="headerlink" title="原子性"></a>原子性</h2><blockquote><p>首先先了解什么是原子性</p><p>学过数据库都知道事务有四大特性（ACID）</p><ul><li>原子性</li><li>持久性</li><li>隔离性</li><li>一致性</li></ul><p>其中原子性是指<strong>一个操作是不可中断的，要么全部成功，要么全部失败。</strong></p><p>通俗的讲就是一场篮球比赛，输了就整队输了，赢了就是整队赢了，不可能存在输的队伍中有获胜的一个人</p></blockquote><div class="note note-info">            <p>让我们通过例子来看看反例 - [举个栗子]</p>          </div><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs java"><span class="hljs-keyword">public</span> <span class="hljs-class"><span class="hljs-keyword">class</span> <span class="hljs-title">IntegerTest</span> </span>&#123;<br><br>    <span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-keyword">public</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">static</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">void</span> <span class="hljs-title">main</span><span class="hljs-params">(String[] args)</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">throws</span> InterruptedException </span>&#123;<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">new</span> Thread(<span class="hljs-keyword">new</span> Increment(),<span class="hljs-string">&quot;黄牛&quot;</span>).start();<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">new</span> Thread(<span class="hljs-keyword">new</span> Increment(),<span class="hljs-string">&quot;狂热粉丝&quot;</span>).start();<br>    &#125;<br><br>&#125;<br><br><span class="hljs-class"><span class="hljs-keyword">class</span> <span class="hljs-title">Increment</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">implements</span> <span class="hljs-title">Runnable</span></span>&#123;<br><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">static</span> Integer count = <span class="hljs-number">0</span>;<br><br>    <span class="hljs-meta">@Override</span><br>    <span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-keyword">public</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">void</span> <span class="hljs-title">run</span><span class="hljs-params">()</span> </span>&#123;<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">while</span> (count &lt;= <span class="hljs-number">50</span>)&#123;<br>            System.out.println(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;当前直播间人数: &quot;</span> + (count++) + <span class="hljs-string">&quot; 人&quot;</span>);<br>            <span class="hljs-keyword">try</span> &#123;<br>                TimeUnit.SECONDS.sleep(<span class="hljs-number">1</span>);<br>            &#125; <span class="hljs-keyword">catch</span> (InterruptedException e) &#123;<br>                e.printStackTrace();<br>            &#125;<br>        &#125;<br>    &#125;<br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>实验结果：</strong></p><p><img src="/2021/08/30/AtomicInteger%E8%87%AA%E6%88%91%E7%90%86%E8%A7%A3%E4%B8%8E%E5%AE%9E%E8%B7%B5/image-20210831165521914.png" alt="测试结果"></p><p>发现当两个线程同时进入直播间的时候，Integer认为是同一个人，实际上是3个人但只显示了2个人，这就不符合逻辑了。这时候就拿出神器<code>AtomicInteger</code>！！！</p><h2 id="简单看源码"><a href="#简单看源码" class="headerlink" title="简单看源码"></a>简单看源码</h2><ul><li><p>通过大致浏览源码发现<code>AtomicInteger</code>底层是使用<code>Unsafe</code>类实现的，当我们点进<code>Unsafe</code>类中发现发放都是Native本地方法，涉及到了C部分**[溜了溜了]**</p></li><li><p>还发现有一个<code>private volatile int value</code>，<code>volatile</code>我仅知道是用来修饰变量标识原子属性**[留下了没有技术的眼泪]**</p></li><li><p>还有用到反射获取AtomicInteger的属性value<img src="/2021/08/30/AtomicInteger%E8%87%AA%E6%88%91%E7%90%86%E8%A7%A3%E4%B8%8E%E5%AE%9E%E8%B7%B5/image-20210831170434897.png" alt="源码"></p></li><li><p>接下来就是提供了两个构造方法</p><ul><li>一个是无参构造，初始值为0</li><li>一个是有参构造，初始值由我们自行传参决定</li></ul><p><img src="/2021/08/30/AtomicInteger%E8%87%AA%E6%88%91%E7%90%86%E8%A7%A3%E4%B8%8E%E5%AE%9E%E8%B7%B5/image-20210831170634705.png" alt="源码"></p></li><li><p>然后就是各种getAndSet/getAndIncement/getAndAdd…总之就是三个单词拼拼拼。讲讲不一样的地方</p><ul><li><code>getAndIncemrnt()</code>和<code>incrementAndGet() </code><strong>前者是返回+1前的值，后者是返回更新后的值。</strong>通俗的讲就是<code>count++</code>与<code>++count</code>的意思嘛</li><li><code>addAndGet(int delta)</code>和<code>incrementAndGet() </code><strong>前者是可以在指定加多少，后者是固定+1</strong></li><li>其余都是一样的道理。。。</li></ul></li><li><p><code>public final boolean compareAndSet(int expect, int update)</code>这是<strong>著名的CAS也就是乐观锁</strong>，两个参数一个是期望值，一个是更新值。如果当前值与期望值一样则更新成传入的update值，否则不更新。</p></li><li><p>还提供了<code>AutomicInteger</code>转基本类型的方法 <code>toString()/intValue()/doubleValue</code>…</p></li></ul><div class="note note-info">            <p>那就使用<code>AtomicInteger</code>来解决上面的问题吧 [我还举个栗子]</p>          </div><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs java"><span class="hljs-class"><span class="hljs-keyword">class</span> <span class="hljs-title">Increment</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">implements</span> <span class="hljs-title">Runnable</span></span>&#123;<br><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">static</span> AtomicInteger count = <span class="hljs-keyword">new</span> AtomicInteger();<br><br>    <span class="hljs-meta">@Override</span><br>    <span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-keyword">public</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">void</span> <span class="hljs-title">run</span><span class="hljs-params">()</span> </span>&#123;<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">while</span> (count.get() &lt;= <span class="hljs-number">30</span>)&#123;<br>            System.out.println(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;当前直播间人数: &quot;</span> + (count.incrementAndGet()) + <span class="hljs-string">&quot; 人&quot;</span>);<br>            <span class="hljs-keyword">try</span> &#123;<br>                TimeUnit.SECONDS.sleep(<span class="hljs-number">1</span>);<br>            &#125; <span class="hljs-keyword">catch</span> (InterruptedException e) &#123;<br>                e.printStackTrace();<br>            &#125;<br>        &#125;<br>    &#125;<br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>实践结果：</strong></p><p><img src="/2021/08/30/AtomicInteger%E8%87%AA%E6%88%91%E7%90%86%E8%A7%A3%E4%B8%8E%E5%AE%9E%E8%B7%B5/image-20210831172549964.png" alt="结果"></p><p>怎么顺序反了…但解决了相同数字的问题！！</p><div class="note note-danger">            <p>我还发现会超出我设置的直播人数</p><p><img src="/2021/08/30/AtomicInteger%E8%87%AA%E6%88%91%E7%90%86%E8%A7%A3%E4%B8%8E%E5%AE%9E%E8%B7%B5/image-20210831172809800.png" alt="发现问题"></p><p>无论设置多少，总会超出一到两个…<strong>还得再研究研究</strong> </p><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs java"><span class="hljs-comment">//todo AtomicInteger超数量问题</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>          </div><blockquote><p>最后来句名言 共勉</p></blockquote><p><img src="/2021/08/30/AtomicInteger%E8%87%AA%E6%88%91%E7%90%86%E8%A7%A3%E4%B8%8E%E5%AE%9E%E8%B7%B5/image-20210831173053847.png" alt="汉叔语录"></p>]]></content>
    
    
